HEADWORD: Chromophotograph
<hw>Chro`mo*pho"to*graph</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/
color + <ets>photograph</ets>.]</ety> <def>A picture made by any of the
processes for reproducing photographs in colors; a color
photograph.</def> -- <wordforms><wf>Chro`mo*pho`to*graph"ic</wf>
